* More generic routing rule.
* Uses a Regex match function.
* Can also pass a format for file type (json, xml etc.)

```ruby
:controller/:action/:id
match ':controller(/:action(/:id))', :via => :get
```

```ruby
match ':controller(/:action(/:id(.:format)))', ;via => :get
```